// 3. ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ì‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÄ‡∏ã‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πå‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô (Weighted Logic)
document.getElementById('submit-btn').onclick = () => {
    const checked = document.querySelectorAll('input[type="radio"]:checked');
    if(checked.length < 40) return alert(`‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏ö‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö ‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏Å ${40 - checked.length} ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠`);

    // 3.1 ‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ‡∏Ñ‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏∞ ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ñ‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏°
    let skillScores = { math:0, science:0, logic:0, lang:0, social:0, creative:0, active:0, detail:0 };
    let skillCounts = { math:0, science:0, logic:0, lang:0, social:0, creative:0, active:0, detail:0 };

    questions.forEach((q, idx) => {
        const val = parseInt(document.querySelector(`input[name="q${idx+1}"]:checked`).value);
        q.k.forEach(skill => {
            skillScores[skill] += val;
            skillCounts[skill]++;
        });
    });

    // 3.2 ‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏Ñ‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏∞ (0-5)
    let skillAverages = {};
    for (let s in skillScores) {
        skillAverages[s] = skillCounts[s] > 0 ? skillScores[s] / skillCounts[s] : 0;
    }

    // 3.3 ‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ì‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏¢ (0-100%)
    let results = [];
    for (let trackKey in tracksData) {
        let track = tracksData[trackKey];
        let sumAvg = 0;
        track.skills.forEach(s => { sumAvg += skillAverages[s]; });
        
        let matchPercent = (sumAvg / track.skills.length) * 20; // ‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏á 0-5 ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô 0-100
        
        results.push({
            key: trackKey,
            percent: matchPercent + (Math.random() * 0.1) // ‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏®‡∏©‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏ì‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πä‡∏∞
        });
    }

    // 3.4 ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÄ‡∏ã‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πå‡∏™‡∏π‡∏á‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î
    results.sort((a, b) => b.percent - a.percent);
    showResult(tracksData[results[0].key]);
};

